title: Yuki Kohara
text:
Yuki Kohara (Japanese: 小原 裕貴, Hepburn: Kohara Yūki, born 21 May 1980) is a Japanese former singer, actor, and idol whose career lasted from 1991 to 2000. He was a member of Johnny's Junior until 15 October 2000.
